{"tid":214953,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)不死J神","createTime":"2017-04-24T05:34:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-24T11:31:29.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bdca0ad05f4e665c5076c01c45bed34f82275dc5","tid":214953,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T05:34:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=8e59832b\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> 按右上主頁可以睇返V台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=1866ceb2\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/d/d2/Death_race_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fd%2Fd2%2FDeath_race_poster.jpg&h=45024480&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/90/Mechanic_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F90%2FMechanic_poster.jpg&h=a0cb3255&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/2/26/Crank_final.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F2%2F26%2FCrank_final.jpg&h=ee3e4bd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.劇情是描述賽車手詹森&middot;安姆（傑森&middot;史塔森飾）被殺手嫁禍入獄後被迫參加最熱門的賽車直播節目，為了贏五次比賽就可出獄的規則在極端險惡的賽事努力求勝的過程..<br />\n<br />\n2.故事敘述一名職業殺手亞瑟&middot;畢夏（傑森&middot;史塔森飾）不但武藝高強、槍法神準，也心思縝密，手法乾淨俐落，在殺完人後會將死者看起來像意外、自殺或被另有人他殺的模樣，以避免警方的追捕。<br />\n劇情一開始，亞瑟聽信老闆迪恩（東尼&middot;高德溫飾）的謊話，誤以為恩師哈利（唐納&middot;蘇德蘭飾）背叛組織，奉命謀殺哈利，亞瑟誘導哈利到了他布置好的現場時，哈利放棄了抵抗，還幫助亞瑟做好自己被劫車的搶匪開槍打死的假象，所以亞瑟心懷愧疚..<br />\n<br />\n3.職業殺手契夫（傑森&middot;史塔森飾）為了心愛的未婚妻伊娃（艾咪&middot;史瑪特飾）打算金盆洗手，但是人在江湖飄，哪有不挨刀，就在他想退出江湖時，仇家上門報復，而且是非常特異的手法：在他睡夢中注射一種毒藥，要讓他心臟麻痺而死。契夫在痛苦中求救，終於發現了暫保活命的方法，作極其激烈的運動，讓心臟猛跳，只要心跳一減緩，他就會死。他要如何保住小命，救出被擄走的愛人呢？<br />\n<br />\n4.上一次大難不死的職業殺手契夫（傑森&middot;史塔森飾）又遇到艱辛萬倍的挑戰，有人將他的心臟奪走，改以一個人工幫浦取代，甚至還有一個不知名的華人黑道組織要取他器官，而這次契夫要一直為自己的幫浦心臟充電，否則就會一命不保，所以他竭盡腦汁，用了變電箱、汽車電池、電擊棒，甚至是靜電來維繫生命，究竟他要如何保住性命，追回自己的心臟呢？<br />\n<br />\n2 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3814595ee12a3559902f2766e607a5f6710e8563","tid":214953,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T05:38:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c02447b2978a481cc45dcedac0e821b8f7e79695","tid":214953,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T06:04:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3968080d82d68d0ad77bcd46434cf202e41a2647","tid":214953,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T06:50:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec20bab69e69ad6e5218a140083f38ac3e3690d4","tid":214953,"uid":7311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T06:52:12.000Z","msg":"咁早播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n番工冇得睇"},{"pid":"8c8eb72d336c4f9579afe6431e426fee23a1a6c9","tid":214953,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T07:21:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/a